DiscoveryOne language driver. Test-harness CLI; see docs/design.md.

Usage: d1 <COMMAND>

Commands:
  lex             Dump the token stream for FILE (one token per line)
  parse           Dump the AST for FILE as a deterministic s-expression
  face            Project FILE onto FACE; print the 2D token grid
  check           Run the facet checker over FILE
  lower           Print the stack IR for FILE
  emit-wasm       Emit FILE as a .wasm module
  run             Execute FILE via the WASM runtime (wasmtime)
  interp          Execute FILE via the reference interpreter
  normalize       Round-trip FILE between layered text and JSON
  facet-snapshot  Render FACE of FILE as deterministic ASCII (for reg-rs)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
